<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-06 01:28 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Top 25 Fared  </HEADLINE>
   By The Associated Press
<TEXT>
<P>
	   How the top 25 teams in The Associated Press' college basketball
poll fared Saturday:
</P>
<P>
	   1. Cincinnati (22-1) beat Alabama-Birmingham 93-80. Next: vs.
DePaul, Sunday, Feb. 13.
</P>
<P>
	   2. Stanford (19-1) beat Southern California 67-57. Next: vs. No.
23 Oregon, Thursday.
</P>
